title: Bushradical behind the scenes....with Special Guest from Season 9 of ALONE. Happy 4th of July 2022

media:group.media:title: Bushradical behind the scenes....with Special Guest from Season 9 of ALONE. Happy 4th of July 2022
media:group.media:description: Hey everybody, I hope you're all having a wonderful forth of July!! Today I'm going to talk about where this channel is at , what I'm up to, the inner workings of why I'm so slow in putting out content, and we're going to hang out with Terry Burns from Season 9 of AlONE......in Valdez Alaska!!!
